c: 4
v: 155
t: "Sidaas awgeed, axdigooda ay ka baxeen darteed, iyo rumeyn la’aantooda Aayadaha Ilaahay iyo ku diliddooda Anbiyada gar darro, iyo qawlkooda ah: Quluubtayada way qufulan yihiin. mayee, Allaah baa yeelay shaabbad dushooda daahda gaalnimadooda darteed marka ma rumeysan doonaan in yar ma’ahee"